works.description: If you are an ardent Elvis Presley fan, here is your chance to own a piece from the personal collection of the Rock ‘n’ Roll king. North Florida & South Georgia’s premier auction house Affiliated Auctions is offering a unique ring that was worn by Elvis Presley in a 1987 National Enquirer contest in its May 1st Fine Antiques auction. The 18k gold ring features a total of 20 diamonds and 23 gemstones. The ring comes along with a copy of the National Enquirer magazine featuring the contest,
